AD, install sealed insulation packages to the interior of the passenger door in accordance with Canadair Service
Bulletin S.B. 601R&hyph;52&hyph;006, Revision `B,' dated December 1, 1993.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
