<!-- PJG ITAG l=83 g=1 f=1 -->
J. Fraud and Manipulation in Connection With Section 4(c) Market Transactions 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Proposed &sect;36.9 applies to section 4(c) contract market transactions the antifraud proscriptions of Sections
4b(a) and 4
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
o
